org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.common.util

Class RMListenerProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.frontend.RMGroupEventListener
      • org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.common.util.RMListenerProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RMEventListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RMProxyUserInterface

    public class RMListenerProxy
extends RMGroupEventListener
    This class adds a cache mechanism that maintains the RMInitialState state of the remote resource manager. You must init the proxy by calling the init(String, Credentials) method after having created it
